    "desc": "VOWS Bridal is a world renowned wedding salon offering both a curated collection of designer special order gowns and off the rack samples. VOWS also carries the largest collection of plus size special order gowns up to size 30. Let our expert stylists help you find the perfect dress that's just right for you.",
